        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "So, as soon as the Farmer had finished planting and had gone home, down they flew to the field, and began to eat as fast as they could.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "He had had experience with such birds before.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000005_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000005_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "But he did not bring any stones with him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000005_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000005_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "He expected to scare the Cranes just by swinging the sling in the air, and shouting loudly at them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "They did not even hear the noise of stones whizzing through the air, and as for words, they would kill nobody.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000006_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000006_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "At last they paid no attention whatever to the Farmer.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "He wanted to save at least some of his grain.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "So he loaded his sling with stones and killed several of the Cranes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000007_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000007_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "This had the effect the Farmer wanted, for from that day the Cranes visited his field no more.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "THE FARMER AND HIS SONS",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "Do not on any account part with the estate that has belonged to our family for so many generations.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "Somewhere on it is hidden a rich treasure.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "I do not know the exact spot, but it is there, and you will surely find it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000012_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000012_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "Spare no energy and leave no spot unturned in your search.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "The father died, and no sooner was he in his grave than the sons set to work digging with all their might, turning up every foot of ground with their spades, and going over the whole farm two or three times.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "THE TWO POTS",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "Two Pots, one of brass and the other of clay, stood together on the hearthstone.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "One day the Brass Pot proposed to the Earthen Pot that they go out into the world together.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "But the Earthen Pot excused himself, saying that it would be wiser for him to stay in the corner by the fire.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "\"Don't let that keep you at home,\" urged the Brass Pot.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000021_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000021_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "If we should happen to meet anything hard I will step between and save you.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "The Earthen Pot could not survive that sort of companionship very long.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8097_282406_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8097/282406/8097_282406_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8097",
        "content": "They had not gone ten paces before the Earthen Pot cracked, and at the next jolt he flew into a thousand pieces.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
